===Taskbot instance installation & settings===

Required packages:
- Python mysql connector (https://dev.mysql.com/doc/connector-python/en/connector-python-installation-binary.html):
  * wget http://dev.mysql.com/get/Downloads/Connector-Python/mysql-connector-python_2.1.4-1ubuntu14.04_all.deb (14.04 ubuntu)
  * dpkg -i mysql-connector-python_2.1.4-1ubuntu14.04_all.deb
- screen (apt-get screen)

You have to prepare to run & build nx_vms projects:
- https://networkoptix.atlassian.net/wiki/display/SD/Setup+Development+Environment+on+Linux

Prepare to start:
1. Create ~/.my.cnf file:
   [mysql]
   host=<TASKBOT UI HOST>
   user=taskbot
   database=taskbot
   password=taskbot
2. Create taskbot folder
   mkdir ~/taskbot
   cd ~/taskbot
3. Get taskbot
   hg clone ssh://hg@hdw.mx/devtools devtools
4. Run screen.
5. Create new screen for your run (Ctrl-A-C).
6. Run taskbot instance
   cd ~/taskbot/devtools/taskbot/instances/linux
   ./run.sh [<NX_VMS_BRANCH>]
7. [Optional]. Repeat pp. 5-6 for other branches 

